  ],
  "remarks": "Aleksandr Lozitsky is a Lieutenant Colonel of the Belarussian military and Commander of unit 65408 / Luninets airfield. He is part of the Belarussian army, which has supported Russian military aggression against Ukraine. In this capacity, he participated in the joint military exercises of Russia and Belarus preceding the military build-up at the Ukrainian border which prepared the Russian military aggression against Ukraine of 24 February 2022.",
